<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">
<title>نظام رفع المستندات | مستشفيات الحمادي</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Kufi+Arabic:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>

  :root {
    --navy: #1D3461;
    --blue: #1855A4;
    --blue2: #3B7DC4;
    --teal: #4CC6C6;
    --bg: #F2F5F9;
    --surface: #FFFFFF;
    --surface2: #F8FAFE;
    --border: rgba(0,38,84,.10);
    --border2: rgba(0,38,84,.06);
    --text: #1A2332;
    --text2: #4A5568;
    --text3: #94A3B8;
    --green: #34C759;
    --green-l: #F0FDF4;
    --green-b: #86EFAC;
    --amber: #FF9F0A;
    --amber-l: #FFFBEB;
    --red: #FF3B30;
    --red-l: #FFF1F0;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
    --shadow-s: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.04), 0 4px 12px rgba(0,38,84,.06);
    --shadow-m: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.04), 0 8px 24px rgba(0,38,84,.08);
    --shadow-l: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.04), 0 16px 48px rgba(0,38,84,.10);
    --shadow-xl: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,.06), 0 32px 80px rgba(0,38,84,.12);
    --r: 12px;
    --rm: 16px;
    --rl: 20px;
    --rxl: 24px;
    --r2xl: 28px;
    --ease: cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
    --spring: cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1);
    --ease-out: cubic-bezier(0,.55,.45,1);
  }
  *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { font-size: 16px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale; }
  body {
    font-family: 'Noto Kufi Arabic', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Display', system-ui, sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    direction: rtl;
    min-height: 100vh;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }
  button { font-family: inherit; cursor: pointer; border: none; background: none; }
  input, textarea { font-family: inherit; outline: none; }
  img { display: block; }

  /* ── SCREENS ── */
  .scr { display: none; }
  .scr.on { display: flex; flex-direction: column; min-height: 100vh; }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════
     LOGIN - Apple style
  ═══════════════════════════════════ */
  #scr-login {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, #EEF3FB 0%, #F2F5FA 40%, #E8F0FE 100%);
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  #scr-login::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 600px; height: 600px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(24,85,164,.07) 0%, transparent 70%);
    top: -200px; right: -100px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  #scr-login::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 400px; height: 400px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(76,198,198,.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
    bottom: -100px; left: -50px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .login-box {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 420px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    animation: loginEnter .5s var(--ease-out) both;
  }
  @keyframes loginEnter {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px) scale(.98); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
  }

  /* Logo area */
  .login-logo {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .login-logo img {
    max-width: 280px;
    max-height: 64px;
    width: auto;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  /* Card */
  .login-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border-radius: var(--r2xl);
    padding: 40px 36px 36px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
    border: 1px solid var(--border2);
  }
  .login-title {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--navy);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    letter-spacing: -.3px;
  }
  .login-sub {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text3);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* Fields */
  .field-block { margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .field-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text2);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    text-align: right;
  }
  .field-input {
    width: 100%;
    height: 52px;
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--rm);
    padding: 0 16px;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text);
    direction: ltr;
    text-align: right;
    transition: border-color .18s, box-shadow .18s, background .18s;
  }
  .field-input::placeholder { color: var(--text3); font-size: 14px; }
  .field-input:focus {
    border-color: var(--blue);
    background: var(--white);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(24,85,164,.10);
  }
  .field-input.err {
    border-color: var(--red);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(255,59,48,.08);
  }

  /* Tab toggle (ID / Mobile) */
  .seg-ctrl {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .seg-btn {
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 11px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text3);
    transition: all .2s var(--ease);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 7px;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    background: transparent;
    font-family: inherit;
  }
  .seg-btn.on {
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--blue);
    box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,38,84,.12), 0 2px 8px rgba(0,38,84,.06);
  }
  .seg-btn svg { width: 15px; height: 15px; flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* Login button */
  .login-btn {
    width: 100%;
    height: 54px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, var(--blue) 100%);
    border-radius: var(--rm);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-top: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform .2s var(--ease), box-shadow .2s var(--ease), opacity .2s;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(24,85,164,.2), 0 8px 24px rgba(24,85,164,.2);
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: inherit;
  }
  .login-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(24,85,164,.25), 0 12px 32px rgba(24,85,164,.25); }
  .login-btn:active { transform: none; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(24,85,164,.15); }
  .login-btn:disabled { opacity: .6; cursor: not-allowed; transform: none; }

  /* Ripple */
  .rpl { position: absolute; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(255,255,255,.2); transform: scale(0); animation: rpl .5s linear; pointer-events: none; }
  @keyframes rpl { to { transform: scale(4); opacity: 0; } }

  /* Error msg */
  .emsg {
    display: none;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: var(--red-l);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,59,48,.15);
    border-radius: var(--r);
    padding: 10px 14px;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--red);
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .emsg.on { display: flex; animation: shake .35s ease; }
  @keyframes shake { 0%,100%{transform:none} 20%,60%{transform:translateX(4px)} 40%,80%{transform:translateX(-4px)} }
  .emsg svg { width: 15px; height: 15px; flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* Spinner */
  .spin {
    display: inline-block; width: 18px; height: 18px;
    border: 2.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.35); border-top-color: #fff;
    border-radius: 50%; animation: rot .65s linear infinite;
  }
  @keyframes rot { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

  /* Admin link */
  .admin-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--text3);
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    background: none;
    font-family: inherit;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: color .18s, background .18s;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .admin-link:hover { color: var(--blue); background: rgba(24,85,164,.05); }
  .admin-link svg { width: 13px; height: 13px; }

  .login-footer {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 28px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text3);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════
     MODAL
  ═══════════════════════════════════ */
  .mov {
    position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 999;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,.4);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 20px;
    opacity: 0; visibility: hidden;
    transition: opacity .22s var(--ease), visibility .22s;
  }
  .mov.on { opacity: 1; visibility: visible; }
  .mc {
    background: var(--surface);
    border-radius: var(--r2xl);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
    width: 100%; max-width: 420px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transform: scale(.94) translateY(16px);
    transition: transform .35s var(--spring);
  }
  .mov.on .mc { transform: none; }
  .mc.lg { max-width: 680px; max-height: 86vh; overflow-y: auto; }

  .mc-hdr {
    padding: 20px 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border2);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .mc-hdr-t { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--navy); }
  .mc-cls {
    width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border2);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer; transition: .15s;
  }
  .mc-cls:hover { background: var(--red-l); }
  .mc-cls svg { width: 12px; height: 12px; color: var(--text3); }
  .mc-cls:hover svg { color: var(--red); }
  .mc-body { padding: 24px; }

  /* Welcome modal top */
  .wl-top {
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--navy) 0%, #0d3480 55%, var(--blue) 100%);
    padding: 28px 28px 24px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .wl-top::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; top: -40px; right: -40px;
    width: 160px; height: 160px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(76,198,198,.2), transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .wl-logo { display: flex; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 14px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .wl-logo img { max-height: 36px; max-width: 180px; width: auto; object-fit: contain; }
  .wl-name { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .wl-sub { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.5); margin-top: 3px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .wl-body { padding: 24px 28px 28px; }
  .wl-text { font-size: 13px; line-height: 2; color: var(--text2); text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .wl-text p { margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .wl-text p:last-child { font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); }
  .wl-btn {
    width: 100%; height: 50px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy), var(--blue));
    border-radius: var(--rm); font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 9px;
    border: none; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit;
    transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(24,85,164,.25);
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .wl-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(24,85,164,.32); }
  .wl-btn svg { width: 17px; height: 17px; }

  /* Admin lock modal */
  .lock-icon {
    width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy), var(--blue));
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 14px;
  }
  .lock-icon svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; color: #fff; }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════
     HEADER
  ═══════════════════════════════════ */
  .app-header {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.88);
    backdrop-filter: saturate(200%) blur(20px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: saturate(200%) blur(20px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border2);
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
  }
  .header-inner {
    max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px; height: 60px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;
  }
  .header-logo img { max-height: 32px; max-width: 150px; width: auto; object-fit: contain; }
  .header-sep { width: 1px; height: 20px; background: var(--border); flex-shrink: 0; }
  .header-tag {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .3px;
    padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 20px;
    background: rgba(24,85,164,.08); color: var(--blue);
    border: 1px solid rgba(24,85,164,.15);
  }
  .header-tag.adm { background: rgba(255,159,10,.08); color: var(--amber); border-color: rgba(255,159,10,.2); }
  .header-name { flex: 1; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); }
  .header-prog {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    font-size: 12px; color: var(--text3);
  }
  .prog-track-sm {
    width: 80px; height: 4px;
    background: var(--border); border-radius: 2px; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .prog-fill-sm {
    height: 100%; border-radius: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--teal), var(--blue2));
    transition: width .5s var(--ease-out);
  }
  .signout-btn {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
    font-size: 12.5px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text3);
    padding: 7px 14px; border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--surface); cursor: pointer;
    transition: .18s; font-family: inherit;
  }
  .signout-btn:hover { color: var(--red); border-color: rgba(255,59,48,.25); background: var(--red-l); }
  .signout-btn svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════
     MAIN CONTENT
  ═══════════════════════════════════ */
  .app-main {
    max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 32px 24px 80px;
    flex: 1;
  }

  /* Doctor card - minimal, clean */
  .doc-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border-radius: var(--r2xl);
    padding: 28px 28px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-m);
    border: 1px solid var(--border2);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .doc-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--navy), var(--blue), var(--teal));
    background-size: 200% 100%;
    animation: slide-grad 4s ease infinite;
  }
  @keyframes slide-grad { 0%{background-position:0%} 100%{background-position:200%} }

  .doc-row {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .doc-avatar {
    width: 48px; height: 48px;
    border-radius: 14px; flex-shrink: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(24,85,164,.08), rgba(76,198,198,.08));
    border: 1px solid var(--border2);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .doc-avatar svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; color: var(--blue); }
  .doc-info { flex: 1; }
  .doc-name { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--navy); letter-spacing: -.2px; }
  .doc-dept { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text3); margin-top: 2px; }
  .doc-stats { display: flex; gap: 10px; }
  .stat-chip {
    text-align: center; padding: 8px 16px;
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border2);
    border-radius: 12px; min-width: 76px;
  }
  .stat-chip.done {
    background: rgba(52,199,89,.06);
    border-color: rgba(52,199,89,.15);
  }
  .stat-num { display: block; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--navy); line-height: 1; }
  .stat-chip.done .stat-num { color: #1a8c37; }
  .stat-lbl { display: block; font-size: 10px; color: var(--text3); margin-top: 2px; }

  .prog-section {}
  .prog-labels {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
    font-size: 12px; color: var(--text3); margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .prog-labels span:last-child { font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); }
  .prog-track {
    height: 6px; background: var(--border);
    border-radius: 3px; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .prog-fill {
    height: 100%; border-radius: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--teal), var(--blue2));
    transition: width .7s var(--ease-out);
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .prog-fill::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: -100%; bottom: 0; width: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,.35), transparent);
    animation: shimmer 2s infinite;
  }
  @keyframes shimmer { to { left: 200%; } }

  /* Info hint */
  .info-hint {
    background: rgba(24,85,164,.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(24,85,164,.10);
    border-radius: var(--rm);
    padding: 12px 16px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start;
    font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--blue2); line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .info-hint svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }

  /* Section heading */
  .sec-head {
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text3);
    letter-spacing: .5px; text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════
     DOCUMENT ITEMS - Apple List style
  ═══════════════════════════════════ */
  .doc-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1px; margin-bottom: 28px; }

  .doc-item {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border2);
    border-radius: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: box-shadow .18s;
  }
  .doc-item:first-child { border-radius: var(--rl) var(--rl) 0 0; }
  .doc-item:last-child { border-radius: 0 0 var(--rl) var(--rl); }
  .doc-item:only-child { border-radius: var(--rl); }
  .doc-item:first-child:not(:last-child) + .doc-item { border-top: none; }
  .doc-item + .doc-item { border-top: none; }

  .doc-item.expanded { box-shadow: var(--shadow-m); border-radius: var(--rl) !important; margin: 4px 0; border: 1.5px solid var(--blue2); }
  .doc-item.expanded + .doc-item { border-top: 1px solid var(--border2); }
  .doc-item.completed {
    background: var(--green-l);
    border-color: rgba(52,199,89,.2) !important;
    border-radius: var(--rl) !important;
    margin: 2px 0;
  }

  .item-row {
    padding: 16px 20px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;
    cursor: pointer; user-select: none;
    transition: background .12s;
  }
  .item-row:hover { background: rgba(0,38,84,.02); }

  .item-icon {
    width: 38px; height: 38px;
    border-radius: 10px; flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(255,59,48,.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,59,48,.1);
    transition: all .22s;
  }
  .item-icon svg { width: 17px; height: 17px; color: var(--red); transition: color .22s; }
  .doc-item.completed .item-icon {
    background: rgba(52,199,89,.1); border-color: rgba(52,199,89,.2);
  }
  .doc-item.completed .item-icon svg { color: #1a8c37; }

  .item-info { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .item-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.3; }
  .item-type { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text3); margin-top: 1px; }

  .item-badge {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px; flex-shrink: 0; white-space: nowrap;
    transition: all .22s;
  }
  .b-req { background: rgba(255,59,48,.08); color: var(--red); }
  .b-done { background: rgba(52,199,89,.1); color: #1a8c37; }
  .b-note { background: rgba(255,159,10,.1); color: #b06000; }

  .item-chev {
    width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border2);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0; transition: transform .22s, background .18s;
  }
  .item-chev svg { width: 11px; height: 11px; color: var(--text3); }
  .doc-item.expanded .item-chev { transform: rotate(180deg); background: var(--blue); border-color: var(--blue); }
  .doc-item.expanded .item-chev svg { color: #fff; }

  /* Expand body */
  .item-body {
    display: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border2);
    padding: 20px;
    background: var(--surface2);
    animation: slideDown .2s var(--ease-out);
  }
  .doc-item.expanded .item-body { display: block; }
  @keyframes slideDown { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-6px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: none; } }

  /* Upload zone */
  .upload-zone {
    border: 2px dashed var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--rm); background: var(--surface);
    padding: 24px 20px; text-align: center;
    cursor: pointer; position: relative;
    transition: border-color .18s, background .18s;
  }
  .upload-zone:hover, .upload-zone.drag {
    border-color: var(--blue);
    background: rgba(24,85,164,.03);
  }
  .upload-zone input { position: absolute; inset: 0; opacity: 0; cursor: pointer; width: 100%; height: 100%; }
  .upload-icon-wrap {
    width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 12px;
    background: rgba(24,85,164,.08);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 10px;
    transition: transform .25s var(--spring);
  }
  .upload-zone:hover .upload-icon-wrap { transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .upload-icon-wrap svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; color: var(--blue2); }
  .upload-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text2); margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .upload-hint { font-size: 11.5px; color: var(--text3); }
  .file-chips { display: flex; gap: 4px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 10px; }
  .file-chip {
    font-size: 9.5px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text3);
    background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px; padding: 2px 6px; letter-spacing: .3px;
  }

  /* File preview */
  .file-prev {
    display: none; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
    background: var(--green-l); border: 1.5px solid var(--green-b);
    border-radius: var(--rm); padding: 12px 16px;
  }
  .file-prev.on { display: flex; animation: fadeIn .25s ease; }
  @keyframes fadeIn { from{opacity:0} to{opacity:1} }
  .file-prev-icon {
    width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 9px;
    background: rgba(52,199,89,.12); flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .file-prev-icon svg { width: 17px; height: 17px; color: #1a8c37; }
  .file-prev-info { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .file-prev-name { font-size: 12.5px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a8c37; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; }
  .file-prev-size { font-size: 10.5px; color: var(--text3); margin-top: 1px; }
  .file-rem {
    width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;
    background: rgba(255,59,48,.08); border: 1px solid rgba(255,59,48,.15);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer; transition: .15s;
  }
  .file-rem:hover { background: var(--red-l); }
  .file-rem svg { width: 12px; height: 12px; color: var(--red); }

  /* Or separator */
  .or-sep {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
    margin: 14px 0; color: var(--text3); font-size: 11.5px; font-weight: 600;
  }
  .or-sep::before, .or-sep::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border2); }

  /* Note textarea */
  .note-lbl { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text2); display: block; margin-bottom: 7px; }
  .note-req { color: var(--red); font-weight: 400; font-size: 11px; }
  .note-ta {
    width: 100%; min-height: 72px; padding: 11px 13px;
    background: var(--surface); border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--rm); font-size: 13px; color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.7; resize: vertical;
    transition: border-color .18s, box-shadow .18s;
    font-family: inherit;
  }
  .note-ta:focus { border-color: var(--blue); box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(24,85,164,.06); }
  .note-ta.ef { border-color: var(--red) !important; box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(255,59,48,.06); }

  /* Confirm button */
  .confirm-btn {
    margin-top: 12px; height: 40px; padding: 0 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy), var(--blue));
    border-radius: var(--r); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px;
    border: none; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(24,85,164,.2);
    transition: transform .18s, box-shadow .18s;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .confirm-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(24,85,164,.28); }
  .confirm-btn svg { width: 15px; height: 15px; }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════
     SUBMIT PANEL
  ═══════════════════════════════════ */
  .submit-panel {
    background: var(--surface);
    border-radius: var(--r2xl);
    padding: 32px 28px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-m);
    border: 1px solid var(--border2);
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .submit-panel::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #34C759, #30D158, #34C759);
    background-size: 200% 100%;
    animation: slide-grad 3s ease infinite;
  }
  .submit-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .submit-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text3); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 22px; max-width: 340px; margin-inline: auto; }
  .submit-btn {
    height: 52px; padding: 0 48px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a8c37, #34C759);
    border-radius: var(--rm); font-size: 15px; font-weight: 800; color: #fff;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 10px;
    border: none; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(52,199,89,.25), 0 2px 6px rgba(52,199,89,.15);
    transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .submit-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(52,199,89,.32); }
  .submit-btn:disabled { opacity: .55; cursor: not-allowed; transform: none; box-shadow: none; }
  .submit-btn svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; }
  .submit-note { font-size: 11.5px; color: var(--text3); margin-top: 10px; line-height: 1.5; }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════
     SUCCESS SCREEN
  ═══════════════════════════════════ */
  #scr-success {
    background: var(--bg);
    align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 32px 20px;
  }
  .success-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border-radius: var(--r2xl);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
    max-width: 460px; width: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
    animation: successIn .5s var(--spring) both;
    border-top: 3px solid #34C759;
  }
  @keyframes successIn { from{opacity:0;transform:scale(.9) translateY(20px)} to{opacity:1;transform:none} }
  .success-hdr {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy), var(--blue));
    padding: 24px; text-align: center; display: flex; justify-content: center;
  }
  .success-hdr img { max-height: 36px; max-width: 170px; width: auto; object-fit: contain; }
  .success-body { padding: 36px 28px; text-align: center; }
  .check-anim {
    width: 76px; height: 76px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D1FAE5, #A7F3D0);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
    animation: checkBounce .5s var(--spring) .2s both;
  }
  @keyframes checkBounce { from{transform:scale(0)} to{transform:scale(1)} }
  .chk-svg { width: 44px; height: 44px; }
  .chk-c { fill:none;stroke:#1a8c37;stroke-width:2.5;stroke-dasharray:150;stroke-dashoffset:150;animation:drawC .5s ease .4s forwards; }
  .chk-p { fill:none;stroke:#1a8c37;stroke-width:3;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-dasharray:40;stroke-dashoffset:40;animation:drawP .35s ease .85s forwards; }
  @keyframes drawC{to{stroke-dashoffset:0}} @keyframes drawP{to{stroke-dashoffset:0}}
  .success-title { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: -.3px; }
  .success-sub { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text3); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 22px; }
  .success-details {
    background: var(--surface2); border-radius: var(--rm); padding: 16px;
    text-align: right; border: 1px solid var(--border2); margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .s-row { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border2); }
  .s-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .s-lbl { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text3); font-weight: 500; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; }
  .s-lbl svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .s-val { font-size: 12.5px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); }
  .s-badge {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 20px;
    background: rgba(255,159,10,.1); border: 1px solid rgba(255,159,10,.2); color: #b06000;
  }
  .close-btn {
    height: 46px; padding: 0 36px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy), var(--blue));
    border-radius: var(--rm); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    border: none; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(24,85,164,.22);
    transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;
  }
  .close-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(24,85,164,.3); }
  .close-btn svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; }
  .success-ft { padding: 14px; text-align: center; font-size: 11px; color: var(--text3); border-top: 1px solid var(--border2); line-height: 1.8; }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════
     ADMIN SCREEN
  ═══════════════════════════════════ */
  .adm-main { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px 24px 60px; flex: 1; }
  .kpi-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  @media(min-width:640px){ .kpi-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(6,1fr); } }
  .kpi-card {
    background: var(--surface); border-radius: var(--rl); padding: 16px 14px;
    text-align: center; box-shadow: var(--shadow-s); border: 1px solid var(--border2);
    border-top: 3px solid var(--border);
    transition: transform .18s, box-shadow .18s;
  }
  .kpi-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-m); }
  .kpi-card.c-blue{border-top-color:var(--blue)}.kpi-card.c-green{border-top-color:#34C759}.kpi-card.c-amber{border-top-color:var(--amber)}.kpi-card.c-red{border-top-color:var(--red)}.kpi-card.c-teal{border-top-color:var(--teal)}.kpi-card.c-purple{border-top-color:#5E5CE6}
  .kpi-icon { width: 22px; height: 22px; margin: 0 auto 7px; color: var(--text3); }
  .kpi-num { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--navy); display: block; line-height: 1; }
  .kpi-lbl { font-size: 10.5px; color: var(--text3); display: block; margin-top: 4px; }

  .avg-card { background: var(--surface); border-radius: var(--rl); padding: 14px 18px; margin-bottom: 16px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-s); border: 1px solid var(--border2); }
  .avg-labels { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text2); margin-bottom: 8px; }

  .ctrl-row { display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; }
  .search-wrap { flex: 1; min-width: 180px; position: relative; }
  .search-icon { position: absolute; right: 12px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); width: 15px; height: 15px; color: var(--text3); }
  .search-inp {
    width: 100%; height: 40px; padding: 0 12px 0 38px;
    background: var(--surface); border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--r); font-family: inherit; font-size: 13px;
    direction: rtl; transition: border-color .18s; outline: none; color: var(--text);
  }
  .search-inp:focus { border-color: var(--blue); }
  .export-btn {
    height: 40px; padding: 0 16px;
    background: var(--blue); color: #fff;
    border-radius: var(--r); cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; border: none;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; transition: background .18s;
  }
  .export-btn:hover { background: var(--blue2); }
  .export-btn svg { width: 15px; height: 15px; }

  .tbl-wrap { overflow-x: auto; border-radius: var(--rl); box-shadow: var(--shadow-s); border: 1px solid var(--border2); }
  .adm-tbl { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; background: var(--surface); font-size: 12px; }
  .adm-tbl thead th { background: var(--navy); color: #fff; padding: 12px 10px; text-align: center; font-weight: 700; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 11px; }
  .adm-tbl tbody tr { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border2); cursor: pointer; transition: background .12s; }
  .adm-tbl tbody tr:hover { background: var(--surface2); }
  .adm-tbl tbody td { padding: 10px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; }
  .s-pill { display: inline-block; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 700; white-space: nowrap; }
  .s-done { background: rgba(52,199,89,.1); color: #1a8c37; }
  .s-part { background: rgba(255,159,10,.1); color: #b06000; }
  .s-none { background: rgba(255,59,48,.08); color: var(--red); }

  /* Det doc */
  .det-doc-row { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; padding: 11px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border2); }
  .det-doc-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  /* Toast */
  .toast {
    position: fixed; bottom: 28px; left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(72px); opacity: 0;
    background: var(--navy); color: #fff;
    padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 30px;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.18);
    z-index: 2000; white-space: nowrap;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    transition: transform .38s var(--spring), opacity .26s ease;
  }
  .toast.on { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
  .toast.ts { background: #1a8c37; }
  .toast.te { background: var(--red); }
  .toast.tw { background: #b06000; }
  .toast svg { width: 15px; height: 15px; }

  /* Page footer */
  .page-ft { text-align: center; padding: 18px; font-size: 11px; color: var(--text3); line-height: 1.9; border-top: 1px solid var(--border2); }

  @media(max-width:580px){
    .doc-card,.submit-panel{ padding:20px 16px; }
    .login-card{ padding:28px 20px 24px; }
    .doc-row{flex-wrap:wrap} .doc-stats{width:100%}
    .app-main,.adm-main{padding-left:14px;padding-right:14px}
    .success-body{padding:28px 18px}
    .wl-body{padding:20px 20px 24px}
    .mc-body{padding:20px}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>


<div id="scr-login" class="scr on">
  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-direction:column;flex:1;padding:40px 20px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;min-height:100vh;background:linear-gradient(160deg,#EEF3FB 0%,#F2F5FA 40%,#E8F0FE 100%)">
    <div style="position:absolute;width:600px;height:600px;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(24,85,164,.07) 0%,transparent 70%);top:-200px;right:-100px;pointer-events:none"></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;width:400px;height:400px;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(76,198,198,.06) 0%,transparent 70%);bottom:-100px;left:-50px;pointer-events:none"></div>

    <div class="login-box">
      <!-- Logo above card -->
      <div class="login-logo">
        <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="مستشفيات الحمادي">
      </div>

      <!-- Card -->
      <div class="login-card">
        <div class="login-title">نظام رفع المستندات</div>
        <div class="login-sub">يرجى تسجيل الدخول للمتابعة</div>

        <!-- Seg ctrl -->
        <div class="seg-ctrl">
          <button class="seg-btn on" id="t-id" onclick="swTab('id')">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.8" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 9h3.75M15 12h3.75M15 15h3.75M4.5 19.5h15a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25V6.75A2.25 2.25 0 0019.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 004.5 19.5zm6-10.125a1.875 1.875 0 11-3.75 0 1.875 1.875 0 013.75 0zm1.294 6.336a6.721 6.721 0 01-3.17.789 6.721 6.721 0 01-3.168-.789 3.376 3.376 0 016.338 0z"/></svg>
            الرقم الوظيفي
          </button>
          <button class="seg-btn" id="t-mob" onclick="swTab('mob')">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.8" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 6.75c0 8.284 6.716 15 15 15h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-1.372c0-.516-.351-.966-.852-1.091l-4.423-1.106c-.44-.11-.902.055-1.173.417l-.97 1.293c-.282.376-.769.542-1.21.38a12.035 12.035 0 01-7.143-7.143c-.162-.441.004-.928.38-1.21l1.293-.97c.363-.271.527-.734.417-1.173L6.963 3.102a1.125 1.125 0 00-1.091-.852H4.5A2.25 2.25 0 002.25 4.5v2.25z"/></svg>
            رقم الجوال
          </button>
        </div>

        <!-- Field: ID -->
        <div id="div-id" class="field-block">
          <label class="field-label">الرقم الوظيفي</label>
          <input class="field-input" id="f-id" type="text" inputmode="numeric"
            placeholder="أدخل رقمك الوظيفي" maxlength="10" autocomplete="off">
        </div>

        <!-- Field: Mobile -->
        <div id="div-mob" class="field-block" style="display:none">
          <label class="field-label">رقم الجوال</label>
          <input class="field-input" id="f-mob" type="text" inputmode="numeric"
            placeholder="05XXXXXXXX" maxlength="10" autocomplete="off">
        </div>

        <!-- Error -->
        <div class="emsg" id="lg-err">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.8" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m-9.303 3.376c-.866 1.5.217 3.374 1.948 3.374h14.71c1.73 0 2.813-1.874 1.948-3.374L13.949 3.378c-.866-1.5-3.032-1.5-3.898 0L2.697 16.126zM12 15.75h.007v.008H12v-.008z"/></svg>
          <span id="lg-em">لم يتم العثور على بياناتك.</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Login btn -->
        <button class="login-btn" id="lg-btn" onclick="doLogin()">
          <span id="lg-bt">تسجيل الدخول</span>
          <span class="spin" id="lg-sp" style="display:none"></span>
        </button>

        <!-- Admin link -->
        <button class="admin-link" onclick="openAdmMod()">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.8" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.5 10.5V6.75a4.5 4.5 0 10-9 0v3.75m-.75 11.25h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25z"/></svg>
          دخول الإدارة
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="login-footer">
        <div>جميع الحقوق محفوظة &copy; مستشفيات الحمادي</div>
        <div>Al Hammadi Hospitals</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="mov" id="wl-mod">
  <div class="mc">
    <div class="wl-top">
      <div class="wl-logo"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Al Hammadi"></div>
      <div class="wl-name" id="wl-nm">مرحباً</div>
      <div class="wl-sub">نظام رفع المستندات</div>
    </div>
    <div class="wl-body">
      <div class="wl-text">
        <p>نرحب بكم في نظام رفع المستندات.</p>
        <p>يرجى استكمال رفع الملفات المطلوبة، أو كتابة ملاحظة في حال تعذر توفير أي مستند.</p>
        <p>نشكر لكم تعاونكم.</p>
      </div>
      <button class="wl-btn" onclick="closeWlMod()">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" style="width:17px;height:17px"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 16.5v2.25A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75V16.5m-13.5-9L12 3m0 0l4.5 4.5M12 3v13.5"/></svg>
        بدء رفع الملفات
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="mov" id="adm-mod" onclick="if(event.target===this)closeAdmMod()">
  <div class="mc">
    <div class="mc-hdr">
      <span class="mc-hdr-t">دخول الإدارة</span>
      <button class="mc-cls" onclick="closeAdmMod()">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
